Summary: Unusual shape UFO seen above building near Birmingham.
Object Flight Path: Path with directional change,Path then hovering
divs: Sighting DetailsI looked over from my car window when i was parked waiting to pick someone up and i noticed an object moving across the skyline above a building, i got my phone out and opened the camera option and took a photo of the object, i looked at the picture but the object had not shown up and therefore i lifted it back up to take another more zoomed in photo and just as i was doing this the object changed direction and disappeared. The object looked like a line with two lines crossing it, i have attatched a picture of the shape of the UFO as it was so unusual and i would love to hear if another of this shape has ever been captured. The object moved in stages, travelling quickly then pausing then continuing moving, it suddenly turned once i was taking the second picture and disappeared. Email: busybunny@live.co.uk
